## **üöÄ Example Workflow**
```python
from notes_io import create_file, write_chunk, read_file

# 1. Create a file
create_file("todo", "Shopping List")

# 2. Write chunks
write_chunk("todo", "Shopping List", b"- Milk\n- Eggs", 0)
write_chunk("todo", "Shopping List", b"- Bread", 1)

# 3. Read full file
title, content = read_file("todo")
print(title)    # "Shopping List"
print(content)  # b"- Milk\n- Eggs\x00\x00...- Bread\x00\x00..."
```

